<h4>My User Centered Design Philosophy</h4>
<p>Users know what they want. They just don't have the skills, knowledge, or abilities to communicate what they want. The challenge faced by the UCD professional is to act as an interpreter on the behalf of the user. The UCD professional interprets the qualitative and quantitative data obtained from UX tests and attempts to understand the user's mental model in order to conceptualize design improvements to system that center around the user's objectives and desires.<p>